{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-440-gcd-and-tiling","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 440: GCD na kuweka vigae","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Želimo potpuno popločati tablu dužine $n$ i širine 1 koristeći pločice dimenzija 1 × 2 ili pločice dimenzija 1 × 1 sa jednom decimalnom cifrom na njima:</p>\n<img alt=\"ten blocks 1x1 with single decimal digit on top, and 1x2 block\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/gcd-and-tiling-1.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Na primer, evo nekoliko načina za popločavanje table dužine $n = 8$:</p>\n<img alt=\"examples of ways to tile a board of length n = 8\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/gcd-and-tiling-2.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka je $T(n)$ broj načina za postavljanje pločica na dasku dužine $n$, kako je opisano iznad.</p>\n<p>Kwa mfano, $T(1) = 10$ na $T(2) = 101$.</p>\n<p>Neka je $S(L)$ trostruki zbir $\\sum_{a, b, c} gcd(T(c^a), T(c^b))$ za $1 ≤ a, b, c ≤ L$.</p>\n<p>Na primer:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; S(2) = 10\\,444 \\\\\n&#x26; S(3) = 1\\,292\\,115\\,238\\,446\\,807\\,016\\,106\\,539\\,989 \\\\\n&#x26; S(4)\\bmod 987\\,898\\,789 = 670\\,616\\,280.\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $S(2000)\\bmod 987\\,898\\,789$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5241000cf542c510037","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302112,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-440-gcd-and-tiling"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function gcdAndTiling() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ngcdAndTiling();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>gcdAndTiling()</code> should return <code>970746056</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(gcdAndTiling(), 970746056);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-440-gcd-and-tiling","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-441-the-inverse-summation-of-coprime-couples","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-439-sum-of-sum-of-divisors","id":"5900f5241000cf542c510037","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-440-gcd-and-tiling"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}